title: BRIEF-Santos Ltd Says Completed Baxter Flow Test In Dorado-3 Exceeds Expectations

BRIEF-Santos Ltd Says Completed Baxter Flow Test In Dorado-3 Exceeds Expectations

Commodities 3 minutes ago (Sep 23, 2019 11:30)

BRIEF-Santos Ltd Says Completed Baxter Flow Test In Dorado-3 Exceeds Expectations Sept 23 (Reuters) - Santos Ltd : * COMPLETED BAXTER FLOW TEST IN DORADO-3 EXCEEDS EXPECTATIONS * SANTOS - MULTI-RATE FLOW TESTING OF DORADO FIELD IN BEDOUT BASIN CONFIRMED EXCELLENT PRODUCTIVITY FROM BAXTER GAS AND CONDENSATE RESERVOIR * PRODUCTION WAS LIMITED BY SURFACE EQUIPMENT CONSTRAINTS INDICATING RESERVOIR HAS CAPACITY TO FLOW AT SIGNIFICANTLY HIGHER RATES * PRELIMINARY INTERPRETATION OF WELL TEST POINTS TO RESERVOIR QUALITY AND CONDENSATE GAS RATIO BETTER THAN INITIALLY EXPECTED

BRIEF-Santos Ltd Says Completed Baxter Flow Test In Dorado-3 Exceeds Expectations
